casebody.data:
Monday, April 26, 1999

MOTION DOCKET

99-157. Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Bailey.

Upon consideration of respondent’s motion to strike motion for order to show cause,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to strike be, and hereby is, denied.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that respondent may file a response to the motion for order to show cause within ten days from the date of this entry.
